data.description: "Welcome to your dream home! This charming 3 bedroom 2 bath home is a must-see, brand new flooring and fresh paint throughout. home is equipped with state-of-the-art solar panels, ensuring energy efficiency and lower utility bills, also comes with water softener. Interior was beautifully designed and it boasts a larger backyard. Also, walking distance the elementary school, playground, skate park and pool. Close proximity to UTSA, Medical center and shopping centers.
